  answer: sydney Opera House
  answerPortuguese: "\xD3pera de Sydney"
  hints:
  - "Designed by the Danish architect J\xF8rn Utzon, this building is celebrated
    for its innovative and groundbreaking design."
  - This iconic structure is renowned for its distinctive sail-like design.
  - Situated on Bennelong Point in Sydney Harbor, it offers breathtaking views of
    the harbor.
  hintsPortuguese:
  - "Projetado pelo arquiteto dinamarqu\xEAs J\xF8rn Utzon, este edif\xEDcio \xE9
    celebrado por seu design inovador e revolucion\xE1rio."
  - "Essa estrutura ic\xF4nica \xE9 conhecida por seu design singular, semelhante
    a uma vela."
  - Situado em Bennelong Point, no porto de Sydney, oferece vistas deslumbrantes
    do porto.
